-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) cleaning one's room<br />\n\t2) running errands across town<br />\n\t3) too much paperwork to fill out<br />\n\t4) having to record all minor details<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tIf Doug were to get into the Club 1997, he would have to do so right when the club opened or when it was approaching closing time, just so he would not have to wait in line. Having his identification checked would be a hassle. Of course Doug had various identification cards with different aliases. He always preferred to remain in the shadows as much as possible. It did not necessarily mean the physical shadow of a shade somewhere away from the sun, although he would not mind that either.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/168171511897/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p799346/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p799346\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p805839/\">你是不是爱错人了？看看这12个迹象你占几条</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p811122/\">八旬老夫妻相守62年被迫分离 这张图看哭一片</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p811200/\">马云全英文演讲谈杭州和G20，高端中国英语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p807011/\">时间胶囊：我想告诉年轻时的自己</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p810038/\">BBC要拍7部高智商烧脑剧，全是这个女人写的</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p810725/\">这个穿大裤衩啃薯条的“